Stanley Capital Management





Stanley Capital Management Profile
	       
		   
		 
Stanley Capital manages a private investment partnership exclusively for qualified investors. We invite a limited number of partners to invest alongside our own capital with a 0% management fee plus 20% of any profits. Our uncommon alignment of interests was inspired by the operating principles and fee structure of Warren Buffett’s 1950s investment partnership. Our mission is to deliver full-cycle after-tax results that are superior to the returns of stocks, bonds, hedge funds and cash while minimizing the risk of a permanent loss of capital. The minimum investment for qualified investors is $1 million. Stanley Capital Management is an SEC registered investment adviser.
		    
    


